                    <p>VISIT</p>
                    <h2>The City Palace</h2>
                    <p>
                        The City Palace Museum in Jaipur displays royal artifacts, textiles, and weaponry from Rajasthan's history. Visitors can admire the beautiful architecture and explore highlights like the Diwan-i-Khas and Peacock Gate.
                    </p>
                </div>
